n+1
\begin{align*}\sum_{i=0}^{n+1} 3^i &=\sum_{i=0}^n 3^i +3^{n+1}=^{\text{assumption of inductive step}}\\&= \frac {(3^{n+1})-1}{2}+3^{n+1}=\frac{3^{n+1}-1+2\cdot3^{n+1}}{2}=\frac{3\cdot3^{n+1}-1}{2}=\frac{3^{n+2}-1}{2}\\&=\frac{3^{(n+1)+1}-1}{2}\end{align*}
